  "body": "<center>\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64a1e7204776b941b5a1eb96\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64a1e73c4776b941b5a1ebb8\" /> <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64a1e73c4776b941b5a1ebb6\" /> <a href=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/wiki/MTPolls\"> <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64a1e73c4776b941b5a1ebb4\" /> </a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\"> <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64a1e73c4776b941b5a1ebb2\" /> </a>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/69849c94ae527b67c278e461\" />\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64a1e7264776b941b5a1eb98\" /> <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64a1e7264776b941b5a1eb9d\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/69849c87ae527b67c278e45f\" />\n\n<details>\n<summary> Full Transcript </summary>\n\nMTPolls\nThe easiest solution for poll management\n\nINTERACTIVE INVENTORIES\nThe plugin allows for a quick and simple way for your players to interact with the plugin!\n\nCOMPATIBLE\nCompatibility without any compromises.\nThoroughly tested on all Minecraft versions to ensure you get the best experience possible!\n\nCUSTOMIZABLE\nEvery aspect is configurable, without being overloaded!\nThis plugin integrates the fully customizable messages protocol. Send clickable components, make chat menus, send URL's and more!\n\nPERFORMANCE\nThe plugin stays lean and mean.\nBy being built from the ground up with performance in mind the plugin uses exactly as many resources as it needs and not an ounce more!\n</details>\n</center>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/views/HiQ5CAMYOg8_EyIDNwIACRscaTcmHwMDKh0MCRs\" />",
